I've re-set them so waitlisted students will only be enrolled if they are declared CS/EECS majors if/when people drop. When the person who knows more about this than I do returns from vacation on Aug 8, she'll look into possible fixes if with her broader understanding of the situation that makes sense.  That means non-majors currently enrolled should see their enrollments as tentative and majors currently (or soon) on the waitlist should be patient.
